Title: Have you already registered for any of these for your creative work?

AnswerList.Title: Australian business number (ABN)
AnswerList.Description: If you have an Australian business number (ABN), you don’t need to apply for a new one. However, you will need to update your ABN details if anything changes. You can use ABNLookup to check if your ABN is current.

AnswerList.Title: business name registered with the Australian Securities and Investments Commission (ASIC)
intellectual property (IP) e.g. trade mark, patent, design or plant breeder’s rights
pay as you go instalments (PAYG) to make tax payments
